	measure R2 = ```
			
			VAR SS_Residual =
			    SUMX(
			        dashboard_dataset,
			        (dashboard_dataset[actual] - dashboard_dataset[predicted])^2
			    )
			VAR SS_Total =
			    SUMX(
			        dashboard_dataset,
			        (dashboard_dataset[actual] - AVERAGE(dashboard_dataset[actual]))^2
			    )
			RETURN
			1 - DIVIDE(SS_Residual, SS_Total)
			
			```
		displayFolder: _KPI
		lineageTag: 2c36dc27-83bf-4434-a343-cc4d85a579ad

